  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to see if the use of a diabetic scorecard during clinic visits
      can improve glycemic control, blood pressure control, LDL-cholesterol, aspirin usage, and
      amount of exercise in adults over age 40 with uncontrolled Type II diabetes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
